Here we present an open dataset of 33 fibromyalgia female patients and 33 paired healthy controls recruited from a Mexican population. Dataset includes demographic, clinical, behavioral and MRI data. The MRI consists of: T1w, T2w, resting state fMRI and task-fMRI sequences. The task was an emotion processing and regulation task based on visual stimuli (pictures). The MRI data consists of raw data in BIDS format.